---

<Layout title="">
  <EventsList
    event_title="Friendship Day"
    event_sub_title="Explore the latest photos from our Friendship Day celebration at ISOE"
    paragraph=` Icon School of Excellence celebrated
                                International Friendship Day with Nursery and KG
                                students through activities that emphasized
                                friendship, kindness, and teamwork. The day
                                featured fun games, group activities, and arts
                                and crafts, where children made friendship
                                bracelets and cards. They also shared stories
                                that highlighted the value of friendship,
                                strengthening their bonds with one another. The
                                event fostered camaraderie and taught the joy of
                                supporting and caring for friends. Thank you to
                                everyone who made the day special, and here's to
                                the wonderful friendships growing in our school
                                community!`
    images={images}
  />
</Layout>
